    <description>Package Description</description>
    <releaseNotes>'Merged PR 11191: solve the build warning for v13.3.7.x'
'Merged PR 11003: [CherryPick] [Ticket 59742] PrimeDevicePowerScalerTestMethod (DPS) initial version.'
'Merged PR 10980: Port 'SpexRMALogger' to prime'
'Merged PR 10493: Prime 13 PrimeSDK'
'Merged PR 10728: porting SPEXADTL to 13.xx.xx'
'Merged PR 10425: VminSearch + VminTC supporting HERMES flow'
'Merged PR 10564: Check MetaNuGet.csproj'</releaseNotes>
